channel.title: [508] system cannot find the path specified
channel.description:
The title of this topic is my error. Here is my run.bat -
[code]@echo off cd ../bin color 40 "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin/java.exe/bulby/Server 43594 pause exit [/code]
The name of my source is ProjectScape 508. It is an edited version of Bulby's source. How do I fix this error??

download the latest java JDK 6 update 14 here…

http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp

after finished, right click run.bat and click edit. change the jdk1.6.0_11, to jdk1.6.0_14.
